    {"Category": "Howto & Style", "Description": "Sophisticated, elegant, and provocative, Harper’s BAZAAR is your resource for fashion, beauty and skincare, culture, and more. Welcome to our YouTube channel! Tune in for skincare tips from celebrities like Rihanna and Ashley Graham on GO TO BED WITH ME. Stay for the hair styling secrets from our favorite stars like Jennifer Garner and Taraji P. Henson on HOW I DO. Get a rundown on go-to recipes and restaurants from our favorite celebrities and chefs like Gwyneth Paltrow and Padma Lakshmi on FOOD DIARIES. And discover emerging stars and breakout talents like Victoria Pedretti and Snoh Aalegra on ON THE RISE."},
