    # Food & Cooking
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "asty The official YouTube channel of all things Tasty, the world's largest food network. Throw your potatoes on the grill this summer, trust @ivskitchen Sponsored by Signature SELECT. #ad We’re the home of your favorite recipe videos and food shows featuring the potato heads you know and love, and all the new fun faces you’ll learn from. Stay awhile and come say hi! Interested in being in a Tasty Video? Apply here to be in our Talent Database: https://airtable.com/shrxXjsfgWbNSDQ2w "},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Welcome to Bon Appétit, where we want everyone to love cooking and eating as much as we do. Recipes you want to make. Cooking advice that works. Restaurant recommendations you trust."},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Welcome to Food Network's official YouTube channel!"},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "For people who love to eat."},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Cook Smarter. Our team of James Beard award-winning chefs, filmmakers, designers, scientists, and engineers demonstrates modern culinary concepts with beautiful, compelling visuals, shows the why's behind the how's of every recipe and technique, and creates innovative technologies that make cooking smarter. We don't tell you how to sharpen your knife, butcher a halibut, or make macarons from scratch, we show you."},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Binging with Babish is the realization of a young(ish) man's dream to combine his love of film and cooking, and to have some fun in the process.  Join us each week as we recreate the foods you've always wanted to try in movies and television - and if you're not careful, you just might learn a thing or two."},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Just a group of mates battling to become awesome home cooks. From our studio in London, we’re joined by millions of passionate chefs and ‘normals’ around the world to explore, learn and have a laugh around food. Each week we serve up three new videos for you to devour - catch them on Monday, Wednesday and Sunday at 5pm GMT. Wanna chat about partnering with us? Drop us an email partnerships@sortedfood.com"},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "Hello, lovely people! Welcome to my official YouTube channel – the ultimate hub for all things food. Here, you’ll find loads of tasty recipes, from quick and easy midweek meals to epic dishes for special occasions. Whether you’re just starting out or a bit of a pro in the kitchen, I’ve got you covered with tips, tricks, and ideas to help you cook up a storm. I’m all about fresh, simple ingredients and having fun with food – as the Naked Chef once said, It's not about me, it's the food! Hit that subscribe button and let’s get stuck in!"},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "The home of Gordon Ramsay on YouTube. Recipe tutorials, tips, techniques and the best bits from the archives. New uploads every week - subscribe now to stay up to date!"},
    {"Category": "Food & Cooking", "Description": "My name is Trevor James and I live to eat and travel.  I live for street food and local food, and I'm traveling to taste it. I'm a hungry traveler that's currently living abroad in Chengdu, Sichuan China,  eating as much delicious food as I can. So far, I've eaten and filmed street food and local cuisine in China, Malaysia, Singapore, and Thailand. Eating the same food as local Chinese, Malaysian, or Thai people has showed me that it's best to travel almost solely for the food! My dream is to keep eating and traveling the world forever, a non-stop adventure!  I live to travel, and I know you do too! I love eating street foods and culinary treats while learning about new cultures! Food is different around the world, and I want to share it with you. Food is something that connects us all, and to me, food is the best way to connect and have a true cultural experience!"},

    # Travel & Events
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Explore Europe with Rick Steves, best-selling travel author and host of public television's Rick Steves' Europe and public radio's Travel with Rick Steves. www.ricksteves.com Rick Steves advocates smart, affordable, perspective-broadening travel. As host and writer of the popular public television series Rick Steves' Europe, and best-selling author of over 50 European travel books, he encourages Americans to travel as temporary locals. He helps American travelers connect much more intimately and authentically with Europe — and Europeans — for a fraction of what mainstream tourists pay."},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "The Blonde Abroad is an award-winning solo female travel & lifestyle brand featuring travel tips, fashion, festivals and photography from around the world."},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Hey guys! I'm Drew Binsky and I’ve been to every country in the world (197/197). On my channel, I tell stories about inspiring people, hidden cultures, and wild adventures in faraway places"},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Hello world! We decided to sell everything and leave home for an adventure around the world. Now, we work full-time as Family Travel Journalists! Thank you for being a part of this amazing journey!"},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Hi, I'm Matt and I run the website, Nomadic Matt. I got the travel bug after a trip to Costa Rica in 2004, and decided to quit my job and travel the world. Since 2006, I've been to over 70 countries on six continents. My advice has been featured in The New York Times, CNN, Time, The Guardian UK, Budget Travel, BBC, National Geographic, Money Magazine, and I am the author of the book, How to Travel the World on $50 a Day."},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "I'm Monica, otherwise known as The Travel Hack. I'm a travel blogger with a love for adventure and stylish travels. Here's you'll find our vlogs, trips around the world, adventures at home and family travels too!"},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "On this channel you can enjoy walking tours of various locations right from comfort of your home.Walk virtually with us through the exotic locations of various cities in 4K UltraHD"},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Hi, we’re Dave and Deb, home of travel, humor, and Canadian pride with a side of biting political satire! We’re award-winning creators. (Forbes even named us one of the Top 10 Travel Influencers in the world!) who bring you the best in travel tips, cultural insights, and entertaining commentary. Whether you’re navigating the snowy tundras of Canada, exploring global destinations, or laughing at the absurdities of modern politics, we’ve got you covered."},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Sharing cheap travel tips on TikTok, Instagram and YouTube."},
    {"Category": "Travel & Events", "Description": "Suitcase Startup is the journey of an entrepreneur taking his startup from the bedroom to the city, with no money, no accommodation and no office.... We will be following Chris as he makes his journey to London to get his business off the ground; the blood, the sweat, the tears...everything it takes to make a business happen in the Capital!"},

    # Health & Fitness
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "We offer at-home workout videos created by certified personal trainers and doctors of physical therapy. In our videos, you’ll see us sweat, laugh, lose count, and modify exercises based on what our bodies are telling us—we have fun with our workouts, and we want you to enjoy yourself, too! No matter your fitness level, if you need help with consistency, motivation, or achieving specific fitness goals, we’re here for you. • Explore our library of workout videos, from strength training and HIIT to yoga • Reach your goals with smart and effective workout programs • Use the customizable workout calendar and personalized stats to track your progress • Eat better with healthy recipes and meal plans built by registered dietitians • Reduce stress with mental wellness resources from licensed psychologists • Interact with our community of like-minded exercisers for support and motivation"},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "WELCOME to Yoga With Adriene! Our mission is to connect as many people as possible through high-quality free yoga videos. We welcome all levels, all bodies, all genders, all souls! If you're brand-new to yoga, check out my Yoga For Beginners and Foundations of Yoga series. These are designed to give you the tools to build a happy, healthy at-home yoga practice.  Do your best, be authentic, and FIND WHAT FEELS GOOD. Jump on in! You don't even have to leave your house."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Build Your Body. Build Your Mind. Build Your Life."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Daily WORKOUT is a videographer ,filmaker and photoshooter company AND WE ARE THE BEST WORKOUT & FITNESS MOTIVATIONAL CHANNELS in BD. SUBSCRIBE and TURN ON NOTIFICATIONS for WATCHING the all new VIDEO "},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Hey guys! My name is Cassey Ho, I am a certified Pilates and Fitness Instructor. Welcome to my channel! I am excited that you are here and I am thrilled for you to start your fitness journey! This channel is 100% focused on you. That's how it should be, right? I want to see you accomplish your health and fitness goals so you can not only look amazing, but also FEEL amazing. How are we going to do that? By helping you find the JOY in fitness! Make sure to hit that subscribe button because let me tell you, you need an accountability partner on your journey and I want to be there for you helping remind you that you can do it!"},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "The brand you know and love as POPSUGAR is now PS, and our popular workout series (including Class Fitsugar, Dance Fitsugar, and Breathe Fitsugar) are now united under a single brand: PS Fit. PS has long dominated the fitness space as the No. 1 source for free at-home workouts on YouTube, and that’s not changing. We will continue to create workouts for every fitness level, including no-equipment exercises, HIIT workouts, yoga flows, and more. On PS Fit, you’ll find videos ranging from five to 60 minutes in length. You can choose to exercise specific body parts and select the level of intensity that works for you. Maybe you want to combine your cardio with dance via a salsa, ’90s pop, or hip-hop workout. If you’re in the mood for stretching, yoga, or meditation, we’ve got you covered there, too. Whatever you choose, you can be confident that all of our workouts are designed and led by knowledgeable and credentialed experts."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Join the Booty Army here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyqR7WkL8i1b6xtSssDmW9w/join Listen to our official Spotify playlist here: https://WEA.lnk.to/tfmAY BOOTIES AT ATTENTION! Get ready to sweat yourself sexy with The Fitness Marshall!! Original Dance Workouts created by Caleb Marshall."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "I'm Daniel Vadnal a physio from Australia. I've been working out for 15 years and love sharing my knowledge. Exercise can be complicated, I'm here to help you."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Subscribe for healthy recipes and quick, effective workouts from fitness instructor, health blogger and new mom, Gina Harney."},
    {"Category": "Health & Fitness", "Description": "Welcome! I’m Natalie Matthews 🤗 IFBB Pro, vegan chef, & fitness model. Join me for high-protein fit vegan recipes, training tips, and a glimpse into my athlete journey!"},

