    {"Category": "Technology & Gadgets", "Description": "Hello! I'm Tom, and I run one of the UK's biggest YouTube channels for technology. We test and review all the latest Phones, Laptops, TVs, PC Hardware, Cars & More - to help you make the right buying decision!"},
    {"Category": "Technology & Gadgets", "Description": "Enjoying the best and worst of new and old technology."},
    {"Category": "Technology & Gadgets", "Description": "Random DIY Projects, Hacks & Mad Science Experiments The King of Random was founded by Grant Thompson in 2012. He had a knack for sharing and discovering the unknown which is why he is forever The King of Random! tragically, Grant passed away in a paragliding accident in 2019. His legacy has since been carried out by Team TKOR! Our current hosts are Jarom Rush, a long time friend of Grant; and Jake Mena (of the channel JakeMakes). Past hosts included Nate Bonham, Cali Gade, and Grace Dirig."},
    {"Category": "Technology & Gadgets", "Description": "Aloha YouTubers, I am The Backyard Scientist! I like to make videos on all the crazy stuff I do. From exploding arrows, to making instruments, molten aluminum to science/chemistry experiments - I do it so you don't have to! I'm always thinking of more stuff to do, if you have an idea, id love to hear it!"},

    # Art & Design
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "The Art Assignment is an educational video series hosted by curator Sarah Urist Green. We explore art and art history through the lens of things happening today."},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "Welcome to The Great Courses Plus on YouTube. The Great Courses Plus is the streaming home of over 18,000 lectures from the world’s greatest professors and experts on history, science, religion, literature, health, travel, and more. Always ad-free, The Great Courses Plus is the place to experience the pure joy of learning—anytime, anywhere. Enjoyed one of our free lectures? Want to learn even more about what you love? Visit thegreatcoursesplus.com and never stop learning with our complete catalog of engaging, enriching courses and lectures."},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "About The Art of Living: Operating in 180 countries, The Art of Living is a non-profit, educational and humanitarian organization founded in 1981 by the world-renowned humanitarian and spiritual teacher - Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar. All our programs are guided by Gurudev’s philosophy: “Unless we have a stress-free mind and a violence-free society, we cannot achieve world peace.” The Art of Living community is diverse and attracts people from all walks of life. To listen to Music, Meditation and Discourses by Gurudev, download the Art of Living App: http://aoliv.in/aolapp"},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "The Artist's Way 🇨🇻 e un komunidadi di artistas ki nasi di amor i kazamentu de Simone (@missmonispencer) ku Sandro(@sandroufonsecacreative), dos artista kabuverdianu. Nos objetivu e apoia artistas na nes kaminhu kriativu, ofereses un spasu seguru i sabi pa es podi konecta, kolabora i konpartilha ses kriason. Ben djuntu ku nos diskubri beleza di arti na Kabu Verdi! ...The Artist's Way 🇨🇻 is a community of artists that was born from the love and marriage of Simone (@missmonispencer) and Sandro (@sandroufonsecacreative), two Cape Verdean artists. Our goal is to support artists in their creative journeys by offering a safe and welcoming space where they can connect, collaborate, and share their creations. Join us and discover the beauty of Cape Verdean art!"},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "Hello everyone it's me Roman Hassan😇 My Chanel introduce Canva to as many people as possible and shows them how it can be use to build professional visual easily. I can tell you about templates, white board & much more and I give information about basic & advanced canva tips & tricks. Canva is a powerful & free design tool that everyone can use to make beautiful visuals.i personaly use Canva every day😎"},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "The world's leading museum devoted to contemporary design in every form. Watch films with the most inspiring figures in design, architecture and fashion at the Design Museum."},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "The Met presents over 5,000 years of art from around the world for everyone to experience and enjoy. The Museum lives in two iconic sites in New York City—The Met Fifth Avenue and The Met Cloisters. Millions across the globe can also experience the #MetAnywhere through our robust website, digital collection, and virtual events."},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "Our mission is to increase the public’s enjoyment and understanding of British art from the 16th century to the present day and of international modern and contemporary art. Tate YouTube brings you videos about art and artists from around the world. Subscribe for interviews with artists, exhibition previews, celebrity art fans, live performance art and more."},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "Bienvenue sur la chaîne YouTube officielle du musée du Louvre ! 👉 Revivez les grandes conférences données à l’Auditorium du Louvre 👉 Retrouvez les présentations des expositions temporaires avec les commissaires 👉 Suivez les YouTubeurs dans les salles du musée 👉 Plongez dans le passé avec les archives du Louvre … Et bien plus encore ! ;)"},
    {"Category": "Art & Design", "Description": "Discover over two million years of human history and culture. Some of the world-famous objects include the Rosetta Stone, the Parthenon sculptures and Egyptian mummies. THE MUSEUM LOVES TO HEAR FROM YOU Here's a quick note on commenting This channel is an open forum where anyone is welcome to contribute. Discussion is encouraged, but please be aware that any offensive, defamatory, obscene or harassing comments or personal attacks of any kind will be removed. Spamming, repeat submissions of the same (or very similar) contributions or content that is off-topic may also be removed."},

    # Parenting & Family
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "The Bump delivers real life guidance to empower new and soon-to-be parents to navigate pregnancy and parenting with expert advice, time-saving tools and a totally inclusive community where they feel supported and seen."},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "Nos programmes sont dédiés aux Parents, aux enfants, à la famille en général. Nous prenons le soin de bien sélectionner pour vous des documentaires ou reportages qui pourront vous aider ou vous apprendre des choses"},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "BabyCenter is your parenting partner, supporting you through your journey of parenthood with a blend of trusted, expert advice, and parent-to-parent tips. BabyCenter is the Web's #1 global interactive parenting network, and has nurtured more than 100 million parents since 1997."},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "A community, a family, a sisterhood."},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "videos so you can learn"},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "With the goal of Helping Parents Raise Good People, we offer expert resources and products based in social & emotional learning for kids & parents!"},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "The Sleep Lady, founded by Kim West, is dedicated to providing gentle sleep and parenting solutions for newborns, babies, toddlers, and even older children who are already in a bed. Our unique approach focuses on comprehensive sleep training that encompasses everything from newborn sleep to sleep regression and toddler sleep challenges. For over 25 years, we have helped hundreds of thousands of families achieve restful nights without resorting to leaving their children to cry it out. Our channel offers a wealth of resources and tips, including guidance on sleep schedules, wake windows, and nap training, to help parents effectively manage their child’s day and feedings. Even if other sleep training methods haven’t worked for you, our gentle techniques can make a difference. Our YouTube channel serves as an evergreen resource, providing valuable content that parents can return to whenever they need expert advice and support on sleep and parenting."},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "I'm Kianna Carissa. This is your go-to spot for mommies' motivation, parenting advice, and adorable kid posts. Let's build a strong and supportive community together! #momlife  #familylife  #parentingtips "},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "Parenting is a journey, and we’re here to make it easier and more enjoyable. Our channel provides practical tips, advice, and fun ideas for every stage of family life. Whether you're a new parent or navigating the teenage years, we’ve got you covered!"},
    {"Category": "Parenting & Family", "Description": "Hi, my name is Ashley! On this channel, I create content for busy parents who want to learn practical tips and advice for implementing Montessori at home with their children. Thanks for watching!"},

    # Environment & Sustainability
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "Inspiring people to care about the planet! National Geographic is the world's premium destination for science, exploration, and adventure. Welcome to the National Geographic community, where we bring our stories, images and video to the world in real-time, inviting followers along on our ongoing 135-year journey. Our yellow border is a portal to the world, showcasing all of the wonder and beauty that it has to offer. This page allows our fans to join us while promoting an enriching and supportive climate for our community. Therefore, we do not tolerate words of hate, harassment or disparagement. We reserve the right to remove any posting or other material that we find off-topic, inappropriate or objectionable."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "The TED Talks channel features the best talks and performances from the TED Conference, where the world's leading thinkers and doers give the talk of their lives in 18 minutes (or less). Look for talks on Technology, Entertainment and Design -- plus science, business, global issues, the arts and more. You're welcome to link to or embed these videos, forward them to others and share these ideas with people you know. TED's videos may be used for non-commercial purposes under a Creative Commons License, Attribution–Non Commercial–No Derivatives (or the CC BY – NC – ND 4.0 International) and in accordance with our TED Talks Usage Policy: https://www.ted.com/about/our-organization/our-policies-terms/ted-talks-usage-policy. For more information on using TED for commercial purposes (e.g. employee learning, in a film or online course), please submit a Media Request at https://media-requests.ted.com"},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "The Guardian brings you news and documentaries about current global issues. The Guardian has been providing high-impact, independent journalism since 1821, always free from commercial and political influence. Help sustain our future by making a contribution today ► https://bit.ly/2Zyt72O"},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "#AlJazeeraEnglish, we focus on people and events that affect people's lives. We bring topics to light that often go under-reported, listening to all sides of the story and giving a 'voice to the voiceless.' Our impartial, fact-based reporting wins worldwide praise and respect. It is our unique brand of #journalism that the world has come to rely on. We are reshaping global media and constantly working to strengthen our reputation as one of the world's most respected #news and #CurrentAffairs channels."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "Watch PBS News for daily, breaking and live news, plus special coverage. We are home to PBS News Hour, ranked the most credible and objective TV news show."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "Welcome to The Weather Channel's official YouTube page. Featuring weather stories and expert insights from the most trusted source in weather. We’re proud to be the world’s most accurate forecaster*, trusted by millions of people. We’re here to help you live safer, smarter, healthier, and happier. What in the weather are you waiting for? Be a force of nature."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "The Sierra Club is America's largest and most influential grassroots environmental organization with more than 3 million members and supporters nationwide. In addition to creating opportunities for people of all ages, levels and locations to have meaningful outdoor experiences, the Sierra Club works to safeguard the health of our communities, protect wildlife, and preserve our remaining wild places through grassroots activism, public education, lobbying and litigation. For more information, visit http://www.sierraclub.org."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "The Nature Conservancy is a global conservation organization dedicated to conserving the lands and waters on which all life depends. Guided by science, we create innovative, on-the-ground solutions to our world's toughest challenges so that nature and people can thrive together. We are tackling climate change, conserving lands, waters and oceans at an unprecedented scale, providing food and water sustainably and helping make cities more sustainable. Working in 81 countries and territories, we use a collaborative approach that engages local communities, governments, the private sector, and other partners."},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "Protecting human health and the environment since 1970"},
    {"Category": "Environment & Sustainability", "Description": "UNEP drives global leadership and forges powerful partnerships to protect our planet. Our mission? To inspire, inform, and empower nations and people everywhere to create a better quality of life—today and for generations to come. Together, let's build a future where progress and sustainability go hand in hand."},

    # History & Culture
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "At Crash Course, we believe that high-quality educational videos should be available to everyone for free! Subscribe for weekly videos from our current courses! The Crash Course team has produced more than 50 courses on a wide variety of subjects, ranging from the humanities to sciences and so much more! We also recently teamed up with Arizona State University to bring you more courses on the Study Hall channel."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "TED-Ed’s mission is to create lessons worth sharing. Feed and expand your curiosity with our award-winning animated shorts - published on YouTube and available with supplemental learning materials on ed.ted.com. Want to suggest an idea for a TED-Ed animation, nominate an educator or animator? Visit our website at: http://ed.ted.com/get_involved. Consider backing us on Patreon. By doing so, you directly support our nonprofit mission to create free, high-quality educational content: https://www.patreon.com/teded"},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Welcome to The Great Courses Plus on YouTube. The Great Courses Plus is the streaming home of over 18,000 lectures from the world’s greatest professors and experts on history, science, religion, literature, health, travel, and more. Always ad-free, The Great Courses Plus is the place to experience the pure joy of learning—anytime, anywhere. Enjoyed one of our free lectures? Want to learn even more about what you love? Visit thegreatcoursesplus.com and never stop learning with our complete catalog of engaging, enriching courses and lectures."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "The HISTORY® Channel, a division of A+E Networks, is the premier destination for historical storytelling. From best-in-class documentary events, to a signature slate of industry leading nonfiction series and premium fact-based scripted programming, The HISTORY® Channel serves as the most trustworthy source of informational entertainment in media. The HISTORY® channel has been named the #1 U.S. TV network in buzz for seven consecutive years by YouGov BrandIndex, and a top favorite TV network by Beta Research Corporation. For a deeper dive, visit history.com or follow @history on Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, and TikTok. For additional press materials visit the A+E Networks Press Center at http://press.aenetworks.com."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Welcome to the official BBC News YouTube channel.Interested in global news with an impartial perspective? Want to see behind-the-scenes footage directly from the front-line? Our YouTube channel has all this and more, bringing you specially selected clips from the world's most trusted news source. For the latest news and analysis download the BBC News app or visit BBC.com."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Welcome to the official PBS YouTube channel! PBS and our member stations are America’s largest classroom, the nation’s largest stage for the arts and a trusted window to the world. In addition, PBS's educational media helps prepare children for success in school and opens up the world to them in an age-appropriate way. Download the free PBS App or head to pbs.org to watch full episodes of your favorite PBS shows, explore music and the arts, find in-depth news analysis, and more. Home to Antiques Roadshow, Frontline, NOVA, PBS News Hour, Masterpiece and many others"},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Inspiring people to care about the planet! National Geographic is the world's premium destination for science, exploration, and adventure. Welcome to the National Geographic community, where we bring our stories, images and video to the world in real-time, inviting followers along on our ongoing 135-year journey. Our yellow border is a portal to the world, showcasing all of the wonder and beauty that it has to offer. This page allows our fans to join us while promoting an enriching and supportive climate for our community. Therefore, we do not tolerate words of hate, harassment or disparagement. We reserve the right to remove any posting or other material that we find off-topic, inappropriate or objectionable."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Discovery Latinoamérica es la versión latina del Discovery Channel, el productor de contenido de referencia mundial dedicado a conectar la audiencia con las maravillas y posibilidades del mundo y satisfacer su curiosidad."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "A&E leads the cultural conversation through high-quality, thought provoking original programming with a unique point of view. Whether it’s the network’s distinctive brand of award-winning disruptive reality or groundbreaking documentary, A&E makes entertainment an art form. Visit us at aetv.com for more info."},
    {"Category": "History & Culture", "Description": "Ve transformaciones automovilísticas increíbles en Mexicánicos, intenta solucionar las enfermedades más raras en Diagnóstico Misterioso, descubre los misterios de la resurrección en Desde la Muerte y acompaña muchas otras series¡Suscríbete para recibir antes de todos los nuevos contenidos!"},

    # Literature & Books
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "The New York Times is the most powerful engine for independent, boots-on-the-ground and deeply reported journalism. We set the standard for the most ambitious and innovative storytelling across features, news and investigations. Because we’re journalists, we’re excited to report the news as quickly as possible, use new technological resources to uncover the truth, and unearth new cultural phenomenons with our critics. The internet didn’t plant these ideas in our heads. We’ve always been this way.  It's all the news that's fit to watch. On YouTube."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "The Guardian brings you news and documentaries about current global issues. The Guardian has been providing high-impact, independent journalism since 1821, always free from commercial and political influence. Help sustain our future by making a contribution today ► https://bit.ly/2Zyt72O"},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "For the good writers and good poets, the non-drumbeaters and non-axe grinders. So long as they're good. We are a quarterly literary magazine that was founded in 1953."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "Atlantic Books is one of the UK's most eclectic and dynamic independent publishers. Join us on YouTube to meet our inspiring authors, discover your next read, learn something new or just rejoice in the joy of books."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "Welcome to New Republic Comics Cards & Collectibles! Please be aware that the content on this channel is for educational and review purposes only. We discuss and review copyrighted comic books, cards and collectibles, but all copyrighted material shown is used under fair use guidelines for the purpose of commentary, criticism, and analysis. We deeply respect the artists and writers who create these incredible works. If you enjoy what you see and want to support the creators, we strongly encourage you to purchase their comic books through official channels. Your support helps ensure that these talented individuals can continue to produce the amazing content we all love."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "The New York Review began during the New York publishing strike of 1963, when its founding editors, Robert Silvers and Barbara Epstein, and their friends, decided to create a new kind of magazine—one in which the most interesting and qualified minds of our time would discuss current books and issues in depth."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "Interviews, profiles, short features, podcasts and much more on the official channel of the Los Angeles Review of Books. http://lareviewofbooks.org"},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "An independent publisher founded in 1973, Chicago Review Press publishes titles of lasting interest and groundbreaking works that reach beyond the trends.CRP has grown into a dynamic midsize publisher with more than 1,000 titles in print. We currently publish about 50 new titles yearly under five imprints: Chicago Review Press, Lawrence Hill Books, Amberjack Publishing, Council Oak Books, and Parenting Press."},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "From BookRiot.com, the largest independent literary site in North America, bringing you news, bookish commentary, and recs for readers of all stripes. Don't forget to subscribe!"},
    {"Category": "Literature & Books", "Description": "Books on Toast is a community for readers, based out of Mumbai, India. We want to create a fun, panel-discussion free space for readers everywhere and make sure all experiences involving literature are actually LIT, y'know? We also do events, so follow us on FB, Insta (/BooksonToast) and Twitter (@BooksonT) to always know wuzzgoinon. "},

    # Philosophy & Thought
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "Self-understanding, calm and emotional maturity. All our content is available on our app and website: www.theschooloflife.com We offer online psychotherapy: www.theschooloflife.com/therapy We publish one film a week, on Wednesdays at 14.00hrs GMT."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "The TED Talks channel features the best talks and performances from the TED Conference, where the world's leading thinkers and doers give the talk of their lives in 18 minutes (or less). Look for talks on Technology, Entertainment and Design -- plus science, business, global issues, the arts and more. You're welcome to link to or embed these videos, forward them to others and share these ideas with people you know. TED's videos may be used for non-commercial purposes under a Creative Commons License, Attribution–Non Commercial–No Derivatives (or the CC BY – NC – ND 4.0 International) and in accordance with our TED Talks Usage Policy: https://www.ted.com/about/our-organization/our-policies-terms/ted-talks-usage-policy. For more information on using TED for commercial purposes (e.g. employee learning, in a film or online course), please submit a Media Request at https://media-requests.ted.com"},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "Welcome to The Great Courses Plus on YouTube. The Great Courses Plus is the streaming home of over 18,000 lectures from the world’s greatest professors and experts on history, science, religion, literature, health, travel, and more. Always ad-free, The Great Courses Plus is the place to experience the pure joy of learning—anytime, anywhere. Enjoyed one of our free lectures? Want to learn even more about what you love? Visit thegreatcoursesplus.com and never stop learning with our complete catalog of engaging, enriching courses and lectures."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "These clips are carefully edited from the full lectures. I watched every single Dr. Peterson lecture at least twice. I hope people can benefit from the unhealthy amount of time and effort I have put into this channel. The clips are easy to share and easier to get into than the full length lectures, but they are not a substitute. Every clip has a time stamped link in the description to the according lecture."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "We feel that even when all possible scientific questions have been answered, the problems of life remain completely untouched. Of course there are then no questions left, and this itself is the answer. - Ludwig Wittgenstein, TLP 6.52."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "This is the best Channel for getting the definition of English vocabularies, terms, and so many keywords."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "Welcome to Encyclopedia of Philosophy! Video about articles on Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy will be posted here! Visit https://plato.stanford.edu for more in-depth readings"},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "Welcome to The Philosopher's Zone, your destination for deep thinking and intellectual exploration. Our channel is dedicated to examining the big questions in life, from the nature of existence to the meaning of consciousness. Join us for engaging discussions and thought-provoking insights from some of the greatest minds in philosophy. Whether you're an experienced philosopher or simply curious about the world around you, our channel is the perfect place to expand your mind and explore the mysteries of human existence. Don't miss out on the conversation – subscribe now and join us in The Philosopher's Zone."},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "I'm giving away a philosophy degree for free! Subscribe to learn and boost your brain power!"},
    {"Category": "Philosophy & Thought", "Description": "The Philosophy Academy is an educational project designed to provide free and high quality education for the study of Philosophy. Philosophy is not only the oldest subject in the world, but it is also one of the broadest and most interesting things to learn about. As such, it is the purpose of this project to eventually teach as much philosophy as possible for our viewers. Whether that be long and broad educational subjects such as Ethics, Metaphysics and the Philosophy of Religion, or shorter and more niche subjects like the Philosophy of Free Will and the Philosophy of AI, we're here to provide free education for anyone interested in studying this incredible subject! "},

    # Spirituality & Religion
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "Official YouTube channel of the Office of His Holiness the Dalai Lama.His Holiness is the spiritual leader of the Tibetan people. He frequently states that his life is guided by three major commitments: the promotion of basic human values or secular ethics in the interest of human happiness, the fostering of inter-religious harmony and the preservation of Tibet's Buddhist culture, a culture of peace and non-violence."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "The Pope Video is a global initiative of the Pope’s Worldwide Prayer Network (Apostleship of Prayer), a Vatican's Official Institution, that spread the Holy Father’s monthly prayer intentions related to the challenges facing humanity and the mission of the Church. Every month we accompany Pope Francis in his prayer requests"},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "Video material about the ministry of the Archbishop of Canterbury, featuring Justin Welby, the 105th Archbishop and Dr Rowan Williams, the 104th Archbishop."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "Rabbi Dr Warren Goldstein is the Chief Rabbi of South Africa and a global Jewish leader.Affectionately referred to as ‘Chief’ and a ‘spiritual entrepreneur’ he has launched and led a number of innovative social projects with global reach and impact. The youngest person to ever be elected to the position, Chief Rabbi Goldstein is a strong advocate for creative, proactive leadership and effective partnership to find unique solutions to the challenges of our time. Two of his local projects have been embraced and championed by world-jewry: Generation Sinai, an annual family learning experience as well as The Shabbat Project which unites Jews annually in over 1000 cities on an unprecedented scale. A qualified Jewish law judge, Rabbi Goldstein has published several books, including his new book, Shabbat. A Day to Create Yourself The Chief Rabbi has a PhD in Human Rights and Constitutional Law and is a regular columnist for the Jerusalem Post and aish.com."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "ПАТРИАРШИЙ ХОР ХРАМА ХРИСТА СПАСИТЕЛЯ РАД ПРИВЕТСТВОВАТЬ ВАС НА СВОЕМ ОФИЦИАЛЬНОМ КАНАЛЕ"},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "John Steven Gaines (born December 31, 1957) is an American Southern Baptist pastor, and the 61st President of the Southern Baptist Convention. Steven Gaines is currently serving at Bellevue Baptist Church in Cordova (a suburb of Memphis, Tennessee), one of the largest congregations in the Southern Baptist Convention. On Sunday, July 10, 2005, the Pastor Search Committee of Bellevue Baptist Church presented Dr. Steve Gaines to the church congregation. At the conclusion of the services the Bellevue family overwhelmingly voted to call Steve Gaines as the seventh Pastor of Bellevue Baptist Church. Gaines succeeds the longtime Bellevue pastor Adrian Rogers."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "The National Christian Council of Sri Lanka was founded in 1945 (forerunners: the Christian Council of India, Burma & Ceylon formed in 1923, the Christian Council in Ceylon, 1922, the Ceylon Representative Council of Missions, 1920, and the All Ceylon Conference of 1912). Basis: To affirm and confess our faith in the Lord Jesus Christ as God and Saviour, and to seek together to fulfill the common calling, to the glory of the Triune God, the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "At the “Women in Islam: Status and Empowerment” Conference: Secretary-General Affirms OIC’s Commitment to Defending the Rights of Muslim Women With Muslim women leading delegations from numerous countries and others with high-level positions in the Islamic world, and with representatives of the Member States, invitees, and experts in attendance, H.E. Mr. Hissein Brahim Taha, the Secretary-General of the Organization of Islamic Cooperation (OIC), stated that since its inception, the OIC has devoted itself to the promotion of the rights and empowerment of Muslim women. This commitment culminated in the adoption by the OIC Program of Action for the Advancement of Women (OPAAW), widely regarded as a roadmap in Muslim societies. This was part of Brahim Taha’s speech before the inaugural session of the International Conference on Women in Islam: Status and Empowerment, organized by the OIC General Secretariat at the invitation of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, which hosted it on Monday, "},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "Welcome to our YouTube channel dedicated to spirituality and religion. Join us as we explore the profound depths of human existence, faith, and inner peace. Through engaging discussions, immersive experiences, and insightful interviews, we delve into diverse spiritual traditions, philosophical insights, and contemplative practices. Whether you're a seeker, a skeptic, or a devout follower, our channel offers a welcoming space for open-minded dialogue and spiritual growth. Subscribe now to embark on a transformative journey of self-discovery and enlightenment. Together, let's uncover the timeless wisdom that transcends cultural boundaries and speaks to the essence of our shared humanity."},
    {"Category": "Spirituality & Religion", "Description": "The mission of Religious Education at Brigham Young University is to assist individuals in their efforts to come unto Christ by teaching the scriptures, doctrine, and history of the restored gospel of Jesus Christ through classroom instruction, gospel scholarship, and outreach to the larger community."},

    # Social Issues & Advocacy
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "The Trevor Project is the leading suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ+ young people. reach out to us at 866-488-7386, text 678-678, or visit TheTrevorProject.org/Help"},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Human Rights Watch is one of the world’s leading independent organizations dedicated to defending and protecting human rights.By focusing international attention where human rights are violated, we give voice to the oppressed and hold oppressors accountable for their crimes. Our rigorous, objective investigations and strategic, targeted advocacy build intense pressure for action and raise the cost of human rights abuse. For over 35 years, Human Rights Watch has worked tenaciously to lay the legal and moral groundwork for deep-rooted change and has fought to bring greater justice and security to people around the world. To learn more about our work or to make a donation, visit HRW.org"},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Greenpeace exists because this fragile earth deserves a voice. It needs solutions. It needs change. It needs action!You are watching Animal Rights Television®. People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals (PETA) is the largest animal rights organization in the world, and PETA entities have more than 9 million members and supporters globally. PETA opposes speciesism, a human-supremacist worldview, and focuses its attention on the four areas in which the largest numbers of animals suffer the most intensely for the longest periods of time: in laboratories, in the food industry, in the clothing trade, and in the entertainment business. We also work on a variety of other issues, including the cruel killing of rodents, birds, and other animals who are often considered “pests” as well as cruelty to domesticated animals."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "The Nature Conservancy is a global conservation organization dedicated to conserving the lands and waters on which all life depends. Guided by science, we create innovative, on-the-ground solutions to our world's toughest challenges so that nature and people can thrive together. We are tackling climate change, conserving lands, waters and oceans at an unprecedented scale, providing food and water sustainably and helping make cities more sustainable. Working in 81 countries and territories, we use a collaborative approach that engages local communities, governments, the private sector, and other partners."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Doctors Without Borders/Médecins Sans Frontières (MSF) offers medical humanitarian assistance to people based solely on need, irrespective of race, religion, gender, or political affiliation. Our teams of doctors, nurses, logisticians, and other frontline workers are often among the first on the scene when peoples’ lives are upended by conflict, disease outbreaks, or natural or human-made disasters.We believe that the principles of impartiality and neutrality are not synonymous with silence. When the world turns its back on crises, we are duty-bound to raise our voices and speak out on behalf of our patients. Our decision to do so is always guided by our mission to do no harm, preserve respect and dignity, and protect life and health."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "The American Cancer Society is the leading cancer-fighting organization with a vision to end cancer as we know it, for everyone. We are the only organization improving the lives of people with cancer and their families through advocacy, research, and patient support, to ensure that everyone has an opportunity to prevent, detect, treat, and survive cancer. We are available day or night, at 1-800-227-2345 or by visiting cancer.org."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Videos created by, for, and/or about the American Red Cross. The American Red Cross is a charitable organization, not a government agency. It depends on volunteers and the generosity of people like you to perform our mission."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "The Sierra Club is America's largest and most influential grassroots environmental organization with more than 3 million members and supporters nationwide. In addition to creating opportunities for people of all ages, levels and locations to have meaningful outdoor experiences, the Sierra Club works to safeguard the health of our communities, protect wildlife, and preserve our remaining wild places through grassroots activism, public education, lobbying and litigation. For more information, visit http://www.sierraclub.org."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Bandela Kranthi Kumar, Advocate at Supreme Court Of India, Founder President of Indian National Yuva Jana Party."},
    {"Category": "Social Issues & Advocacy", "Description": "Welcome to Social Impact Advocacy, where we amplify voices, share inspiring stories, and advocate for meaningful change. Our mission is to empower families and communities through education, advocacy, and technology. Join us as we tackle important issues, celebrate successes, and work together to create a brighter future for everyone. Subscribe for impactful stories, resources, and insights that make a difference!"},

