    {"Category": "Hobbies & Interests", "Description": "Welcome to JCTs Fascinating Hobbies, a place where I tend to post videos, relating to my hobbies, interests and anything else that may be of interest. I have recently decided to try to make my channel a little more interesting, so will be filming my various hobby exploits, and uploading them for the world to enjoy! From cars to computers, retro tech and a lot of things in-between, I cover what I find interesting, I hope you do, too. Feel free to subscribe, and don't forget to like those videos, should you enjoy what you see."},
