    # Mental Health & Wellness
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "Tips, tricks, and insights from my own experience dealing with anxiety and rumination. I talk about psychology, philosophy, and self-help. The videos are narrated by an AI-generated voice."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "Welcome to the talkBD Bipolar Disorder Podcast - where we gather researchers, people with lived experience, healthcare providers, and top bipolar disorder experts from around the world to break down and answer the most important questions about living with bipolar disorder. "},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "Hi, everyone! I’m Stephen, and I’m excited to welcome you to Surviving Schizophrenia, a channel built on hope, strength, and community for anyone navigating mental health challenges. At age 12, I spent two weeks at UCLA Resnick Neuropsychiatric Hospital and was diagnosed with schizophreniform disorder, which later developed into schizophrenia and an anxiety disorder. I live with treatment-resistant, childhood-onset schizophrenia. Here, you’ll discover inspiring stories, practical advice, and a raw yet compassionate perspective on living with a misunderstood condition. More importantly, you’ll find a welcoming community. As I navigate these unpredictable waters, I invite you to join me—share your stories, or listen to the echoes of triumph and perseverance from around the world."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "EDRC is a non-profit organization that links resources, information and support for eating disorders in Silicon Valley."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "The 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline (formerly known as the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline) is a 24-hour, toll-free suicide prevention crisis line available to anyone in crisis or emotional distress. If you need support, call 988 and you will be routed to one of our 200+ crisis centers nationwide. Call for yourself, or for someone you care about. Your call is free and confidential. You can also text 988 or chat with us online at 988lifeline.org."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "The National Institute of Mental Health (NIMH) is the largest scientific organization, in the world, dedicated to mental health research. NIMH is one of 27 Institutes and Centers of the National Institutes of Health, the world's leading biomedical research organization. The mission of NIMH is to transform the understanding and treatment of mental illnesses through basic and clinical research, paving the way for prevention, recovery and cure. NIMH encourages and allows for the submission of written comments. In accordance with the Federal Government’s other social media comment policies, NIMH has instituted the following comment policy for the NIMH YouTube page: http://www.nimh.nih.gov/site-info/policies.shtml#Comment-Policy."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "With more than 157,000 members, the American Psychological Association advances psychological science to promote health, education and human welfare."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "One of the six WHO Regions, WHO South-East Asia is home to over a quarter of the world’s population. Committed to building a better, healthier future for the nearly two billion people in the Region, WHO is working with the 11 Member States to address persisting and emerging epidemiological and demographic challenges. This is the official YouTube channel for the WHO Regional Office for South-East Asia."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "Mental Health First Aid International is a global, purpose-driven provider of mental health first aid education that equips individuals with the knowledge and skills to provide support when it matters most."},
    {"Category": "Mental Health & Wellness", "Description": "Our aim is to promote mental health awareness and positive attitudes towards mental health. We seek to encourage social inclusion for individuals with mental illness, and promote positive messages regarding mental health to the community."},

    # Personal Development & Self-Improvement
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Lewis Howes is a 2x New York Times best-selling author, 2x All-American athlete, keynote speaker, and entrepreneur. The School of Greatness shares inspiring interviews from the most successful people on the planet—world-renowned leaders in business, entertainment, sports, science, health, and literature—to inspire YOU to unlock your inner greatness and live your best life."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Tim Ferriss has been listed as one of Fast Company’s “Most Innovative Business People” and one of Fortune’s “40 under 40.” He is an early-stage technology investor/advisor (Uber, Facebook, Shopify, Duolingo, Alibaba, and 50+ others) and the author of five #1 New York Times and Wall Street Journal bestsellers, including The 4-Hour Workweek and Tools of Titans: The Tactics, Routines, and Habits of Billionaires, Icons, and World-Class Performers. The Observer and other media have called Tim “the Oprah of audio” due to the influence of The Tim Ferriss Show podcast, which is the first business/interview podcast to exceed 100 million downloads. It has now exceeded 900 million downloads."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "The Joe Rogan Experience podcast"},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "The Art of Charm is where self-motivated guys and gals, just like you, come to learn from a diverse mix of experienced mentors, including the world's best professional and academic minds, scientists, relationship experts, entrepreneurs, bestselling authors, and other badasses. This show will make you a better networker, better connector, and -- most important -- a better thinker."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Gary Vaynerchuk is a serial entrepreneur and serves as the Chairman of VaynerX, the CEO of VaynerMedia, and the Creator and CEO of VeeFriends. Gary is considered one of the leading global minds on what’s next in culture, relevance, and the internet. Known as “GaryVee,” he is described as one of the most forward thinkers in business. He is a prolific angel investor with early investments in companies like Facebook, Twitter, Tumblr, Venmo, Snapchat, Coinbase, and Uber. In addition to running multiple businesses, Gary documents his daily life as a CEO through his social media channels, which have more than 45 million followers and garner over 300 million monthly impressions/views across all platforms. Gary serves on the board of MikMak, Bojangles Restaurants, Global Citizen Forum, and Pencils of Promise. He is also a longtime Well Member of charity: water."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Description @TheHiddenBrain190 will give you :- :- I am Sunny r.s. shaw (:The main focus of this channel is to share Inspiring Videos from Sports, Cinema, and Business. ➡️Motivational shorts. ➡️Rich people's mindset shorts. ➡️Entertainment shorts. ➡️Funny shorts & many more I'm sharing these videos for Education perpose. All the Credit goes to there Respected Owners. The videos I am sharing originaly doesn't belong to me. If anyone has any concerns or wishes to have the video removed/ video credit, please feel free to contact me. We will solve it together {Email:- sunnyrsshaw@gmail.com} If you like this videos then please subscribed my channel and keep supporting me for grow my new youtube channel."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Freakonomics began as a book, which led to a blog, a documentary film, more books, a pair of pants, and in 2010, a podcast called Freakonomics Radio. Hosted by Stephen J. Dubner, it became and remains one of the most popular podcasts in the world, with a reputation for storytelling that is both rigorous and entertaining. Its archive of more than 500 episodes is available, for free, on any podcast app, and the show airs weekly on NPR stations. Freakonomics Radio is now the flagship show of the Freakonomics Radio Network, which includes the podcasts No Stupid Questions (est. 2020), People I (Mostly) Admire (2020), Freakonomics, M.D. (2021), and a variety of special series."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Hello! We no longer publish Planet Money or The Indicator here. More info→"},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "My Channel Is Helping For Personal development and self-improvement refer to the process of consciously working on oneself to achieve personal growth, increase self-awareness, and enhance one's skills and abilities. It involves setting goals, learning new skills, building positive habits, and cultivating a growth mindset. Personal development and self-improvement can help individuals improve their quality of life, enhance their relationships, and achieve their full potential in various aspects of their lives."},
    {"Category": "Personal Development & Self-Improvement", "Description": "Welcome to Personal Development, your go-to destination for personal growth, motivation, and self-improvement. If you're eager to unlock your full potential, cultivate a positive mindset, and live a fulfilling life, you're in the right place. Here we believe that everyone has the power to transform their lives and achieve greatness. Our mission is to provide you with the tools, insights, and inspiration to embark on a journey of self-discovery, personal growth, and success. But personal development is not just about achieving external success; it's also about nurturing your well-being and finding balance in life. Remember, the journey of personal development is unique for each individual, and we're here to guide and support you every step of the way. Get ready to embark on an incredible transformational journey with Personal Development"},

    # Children's Content
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "At CoComelon, our primary goal has always been to engage families with entertaining and educational content that makes universally-relatable preschool moments fun. Our beautiful 3D animation and toe-tapping songs create a world that centers on the everyday experiences of young children. In addition to helping preschoolers learn letters, numbers, animal sounds, colors, and more, the videos impart prosocial life lessons, providing parents with an opportunity to teach and play with their children as they watch together. CoComelon. Where kids can be happy and smart!"},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Join Baby Taku and friends for fun adventures as they explore ABCs, colors, numbers, and more. Let’s play and learn together!  ChuChu TV's Toddler Learning Videos are designed to engage kids with fun nursery rhymes and educational songs featuring colorful animations. Our team includes moms and dads of young children, experts in early childhood education, writers, artists, animators and musicians.. We have a global team of creatives to ensure culturally-relevant content for children worldwide."},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Little Baby Bum follows the musical adventures of Mia, Twinkle the Star and Baby Max. Everyday moments like bath time, getting dressed, or playing peekaboo become even more fun with new and classic nursery rhymes. Little Baby Bum is an animated musical show that celebrates early childhood experiences and supports cognitive development through loveable characters, relatable stories and the magic of song, repetition, rhythm, and rhyme."},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Come explore the wondrous world with everybody's best friend, Blippi. How does a recycling truck work? What does a baker do? What is the best playground around? There are so many exciting things to explore and learn. Feed your kids’ curiosity while they learn about vehicles, animals, the natural world and so much more. Blippi helps children‘s understanding of the world and encourages vocabulary development. Blippi loves visiting exciting places such as children’s museums and the zoo! He loves singing, dancing, playing and exploring. His contagious curiosity engages young viewers in learning adventures that help them both grow and develop."},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "The official channel for all things Mother Goose Club. Preschoolers, parents and teachers love Mother Goose Club's six colorful characters that introduce preschool themes through classic nursery rhymes, original songs and colorful videos. Come dance, clap and sing along! The best nursery rhyme videos for children on YouTube! New videos released each week.  Subscribe now!"},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Welcome to The Wiggles YouTube channel, where you'll find all types of toddler tunes - from playful kids songs and classic nursery rhymes, to educational children's music and fun dance tracks! Join us on a musical journey designed to engage young minds and promote early learning. With colourful performances and interactive content, we aim to create a joyful learning experience for children. Little ones will develop essential skills while having a blast!"},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Welcome to The Kiboomers, where learning is fun! With over 3 billion YouTube views and a billion streams across Spotify, Amazon, and Apple, our music enriches families and educators worldwide.Our extensive collection of kids' music videos and nursery rhymes covers everything from ABCs and 123s to colors and shapes, making early learning both fun and engaging. Our Freeze Dance, Floor is Lava, and Going on a Bear Hunt videos are just a taste of the exciting dance songs and circle time activities we offer, designed to make learning a great adventure both at home and in the classroom."},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Making learning fun and simple! With billions of views, Super Simple Songs is a trusted resource for parents and teachers around the world. Our library of nursery rhymes, original songs, and animated videos are perfect for children between the ages of 1 and 8. Each video is carefully crafted to engage young viewers and make learning new concepts such as colors, counting, animals and more both fun and simple! Our channel features a diverse range of fun characters, including: • Finny the Shark • The Bumble Nums • Caitie from Caitie's Classroom • The Roundabouts • Noodle & Pals • Rhymington Square • Carl's Car Wash Our videos are designed to be engaging and fun, helping children learn new concepts and skills while having a great time."},
    {"Category": "Children's Content", "Description": "Welcome to Pinkfong's official YouTube channel. Meet Pinkfong’s fun, educational videos that captured the hearts of millions of children around the world. Subscribe to Pinkfong Baby Shark’s channel for kids’ favorite songs & stories created by professionals in child education."},
